  <summary date="2015-05-11T15:09:45Z" status="Introduced in House">Health Savings Account Act 

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to increase the maximum amount that an individual participating in a health savings account may contribute to such an account to match the amount of the deductible and out-of-pocket expenses that such individual pays under a high deductible health plan.</summary>
